textBeforeTable: Tribes: Ascend, the upcoming jetpack-powered multiplayer shooter revival. They mention new maps and some fixes, one of which should encourage those hoping the game's mechanics will live up to its predecessors: "The speed cap has been removed and various falling, skiing and jetpack physics changes have been implemented, including modifications to Skills."
